{"tid":1687708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"半數市民支持不合作運動","createTime":"2019-11-02T04:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T04:32:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3a0abcad98b67cc639364f364917d3d189b9f97e","tid":1687708,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191102/KMOWET3GQRPI4BUQE3I3RLEVQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191102%2FKMOWET3GQRPI4BUQE3I3RLEVQE%2F&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=cbd93bb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191102%2FKMOWET3GQRPI4BUQE3I3RLEVQE%2F&h=f79c8e18\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191102/KMOWET3GQRPI4BUQE3I3RLEVQE/</a><br />\n<br />\n半數市民支持不合作運動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/tHUkCyi_jXkW5edvtZDZFY3PTsQ=/802x534/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/DCESJDOGYUDWQRP7S5XWEMXO6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FtHUkCyi_jXkW5edvtZDZFY3PTsQ%3D%2F802x534%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FDCESJDOGYUDWQRP7S5XWEMXO6E.jpg&h=bc8fa1b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民調顯示，支持以不合作運動促使政府回應訴求的市民，由一星期前的剛逾四成增至日前的接近五成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港民研】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中運動曠日持久，由遊行集會逐步演化成為堵塞交通等不合作運動。有民調顯示，支持以不合作運動促使政府回應訴求的市民，由一星期前的剛逾四成增至日前的接近五成。與此同時，贊成以杯葛或支持個別品牌或商店來表態的市民，亦由接近五成增至五成半。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究發起由市民挑選問題，然後進行滾動民調的「我們香港人」計劃。最新調查結果顯示，上月25至31日間，受訪的逾千名市民中，48.8%人支持以堵塞交通、罷工等不合作運動來促使政府回應訴求，當中表示「好支持」的人更多達26.9%，比「幾支持」的21.9%多，至於反對不合作運動的人則只有38.4%。<br />\n贊成杯葛品牌者增<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警：維園聚會 逾50人參與即違法<br />\n<br />\n而一星期前、即10月22至24日間，同一調查結果是只有41.5%受訪者支持不合作運動，少於反對的46.2%。<br />\n<br />\n香港民研「我們香港人」計劃名譽總監黃偉國認為，「好支持」不合作運動的受訪者從上星期的兩成一大增至本周的兩成七，顯示市民了解到不合作運動是令政府回應市民訴求的必須手段。<br />\n<br />\n另外，民調亦探究市民對藉着杯葛或支持個別品牌、商店來表達對反送中風波的立場，最新結果顯示，多達55.4%受訪者支持，較一星期前的48%為多，但反對的受訪者亦由32.9%微升至33.1%。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/Mj1E6PHw_0T4veLdH45mdGtRLIM=/802x564/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CFE5VPQUFNTM34SYSFNVXLQOFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FMj1E6PHw_0T4veLdH45mdGtRLIM%3D%2F802x564%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCFE5VPQUFNTM34SYSFNVXLQOFQ.jpg&h=d6934b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"8721af84711a3876a596c3cc2818a38081a6968c","tid":1687708,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:32:39.000Z","msg":"要繼續文宣罷買同黃金經濟圈嘅必要性<br />\n務求推到七成以上<br />\n<br />\n甴種平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}